{"tid":1322123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［又撚大伯］想屈示威者暴力，都唔睇下同邊個講","createTime":"2019-07-16T00:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T11:01:50.000Z","uid":216800,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d5bd9f84b25cd762cd94ea1c984b7a93ed701076","tid":1322123,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:40:19.000Z","msg":"我仲刷緊牙 大伯就買咗啲早餐返咗黎<br />\n咁好啦，大家一齊坐低食早餐<br />\n佢好順手咁打開電視機又睇TBB新聞<br />\n一播到警察衝落威者嗰時就話啲示威者幾暴力 又整傷咗幾個同事喇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">吓？</span> 又勁大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢頭笠笠咁望住我<br />\n我接住講 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係咯！</span>啲狗幾暴力呀！衝埋去咬傷啲人喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大伯聽到之後呼吸咗一下就話 唉，唔係... <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">吓？</span>佢都未講完就大聲吓佢<br />\n唔係啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢已經知死唔敢講 然後繼續食早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哎呀，佢今日心情又唔靚喇 點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPs：佢想洗我腦去符合佢心目中嘅正常，但作為一個曾經比傳銷洗過腦 呃咗我大拿拿500蚊嘅人 大伯嘅洗腦簡直濕濕碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce052c41157a263f8bf16fac30c36ddc79a5af2","tid":1322123,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:45:19.000Z","msg":"一日一撚 會唔會撚到出書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42eb419dba36b133711c2a460f6b2a485ec2c4f2","tid":1322123,"uid":141914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:47:33.000Z","msg":"吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7439089ecff94a9fcb77882c5b18691b60b10547","tid":1322123,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42eb419dba36b133711c2a460f6b2a485ec2c4f2","tid":1322123,"uid":141914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:47:33.000Z",